# 🚧 Traffic Safety Center

A full-stack web application for a real-world traffic safety business, providing services and products for road marking, signage, and traffic management.

🌐 Live Website: https://www.trafficsafetycenter.com

---

## 🧠 Overview

This project was built as a production-ready website for a traffic safety company.

It combines a modern frontend with a Node.js backend, focusing on performance, accessibility, and real-world usability.

The system includes:
- Service presentation (road marking, signage, traffic arrangements)
- Product catalog with categories
- Client-side shopping cart (quote-based system)
- Contact system integrated with Telegram
- Image optimization pipeline for performance

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

**Frontend**
- HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- Bootstrap (RTL support)

**Backend**
- Node.js
- Express

**Other Tools**
- Telegram Bot API (notifications)
- Sharp (image optimization)
- Render (deployment)

---

## ⚙️ Features

### 🛒 Store System
- Product categories
- Client-side cart (LocalStorage-based)
- Quote request flow (no direct payment yet)

### ⚡ Performance Optimization
- Lazy loading for product images
- Custom image optimization pipeline (WebP conversion, thumbnails)

👉 Image optimization script:
See: :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}

### 📩 Contact System
- Contact form sends messages directly to Telegram
- Supports multiple recipients via environment variables

### 📱 Responsive Design
- Fully responsive (mobile-first approach)
- RTL support for Hebrew

### ♿ Accessibility
- Designed according to Israeli Standard (T"י 5568) / WCAG AA principles
- Includes:
  - Text scaling
  - High contrast mode
  - Animation disabling
  - Readable fonts

---

## 🚀 Setup & Installation

```bash
npm install
npm run dev